{"tid":517011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(同性戀議員) 慢必參演香港電影, 片酬1000港元","createTime":"2018-01-02T01:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T03:22:27.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"53f84dd3d05c73714d663cd921f2c5838f434a54","tid":517011,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T01:52:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20171212/563035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20171212%2F563035&d=ZGLzGSuEDofInY%2FLzkwlTMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3d92aeb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20171212%2F563035&h=75e4e134\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20171212/563035</a><br />\n<br />\n人民力量立法會議員慢必陳志全，做過電台節目主持同演員，最近忙住同建制派議員就修改議事規則喺議會打仗，但忙還忙，都抽到時間重操故業，客串拍電影。講緊嘅係由舒琪監製，今屆「鮮浪潮」電影節最佳導演李駿碩首次執導嘅《翠絲》（港版《丹麥女孩》）。<br />\n<br />\n電影講述變性人男主角翠絲，發現自己有做女性嘅傾向，之後逐步去實踐，當中面對嘅困難同壓抑。翠絲一角由剛奪得人生首個電影獎項、國際電影人年展最佳男配角嘅姜皓文（黑仔）演出；新鮮出爐金馬影后惠英紅，會飾演佢老婆。<br />\n...<br />\n其實慢必以往拍過好幾套電影，包括香港cult片代表作之一嘅《生化壽司》，亦喺《古惑仔：龍爭虎鬥》入裡做拳術旁述，演技都唔錯㗎。預計《翠絲》下年會上畫，到時又可以一睹慢必嘅演技喇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171223/s00002/1513965687384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171223%2Fs00002%2F1513965687384&d=ZGLzGSuEDofInY%2FLzkwlTMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=a3893ef6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171223%2Fs00002%2F1513965687384&h=a782d21b\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20171223/s00002/1513965687384</a><br />\n<br />\n幾位議員喺抽獎環節亦預備唔少禮物同現金獎，抽晒後Miss Mo即席再拎多1000蚊出嚟抽，<strong>慢必亦攞咗早前為港版丹麥女孩拍戲所得嘅1000元片酬出嚟再抽獎</strong>，相信助理都皆大歡喜，開心過聖誕。"},{"pid":"879fc8e38e1af1d58b84fa1105aa1fb3b168fef5","tid":517011,"uid":16161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T01:54:03.000Z","msg":"姜皓文同惠英紅做夫妻好似怪怪地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c43e3257607c8a808eaea7efe702687d4a6fac4","tid":517011,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T01:55:26.000Z","msg":"話哂都係專業演員，一千蚊太小啦"},{"pid":"3099bba9ae211e5141b60ffd842c29aa0f53f7cd","tid":517011,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c43e3257607c8a808eaea7efe702687d4a6fac4","tid":517011,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T01:55:26.000Z","msg":"話哂都係專業演員，一千蚊太小啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T01:58:58.000Z","msg":"呢套片唔係中港合拍片, 低成本, 無法子...<br />\n<br />\n(係中港合拍片, 就算係無對白既大茄, 都可以片酬過萬.....)"},{"pid":"8ae290d05daeee362dd3e711d7fefde0a1520c45","tid":517011,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T01:59:55.000Z","msg":"變性人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0185bfd9276bf5f983687b4e60391f9f712563df","tid":517011,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e67d3477cb16758e497977dc7479695e858998","tid":517011,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49be7b267bb49412b477665af55073f911482851","tid":517011,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76d97c797c7da1f93f3feb1369d264f1d4ad46a","tid":517011,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T03:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}